-- Petropavlovsk May Raise $300 Million in Its IRC Unit Offering, Hambro Says
-- B y   A m a n d a   J o r d a n
-- 2010-10-05T05:30:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-05/petropavlovsk-may-raise-300-million-in-its-irc-unit-offering-hambro-says.html
Petropavlovsk Plc, Russia’s third-
largest gold producer, plans to raise about $300 million by
selling shares in its IRC Ltd. iron-ore unit in Hong Kong this
month, Chairman Peter Hambro said today in a Bloomberg
Television interview.  The company is seeing “very good demand” for the initial
public offering, Hambro said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
